(42, 18, 18, 44, 16, 30, 30, 'what shall I do to inherit eternal life', 'Inquiry About Salvation', 'Both passages emphasize a question about salvation. The ruler in Luke asks what to do to inherit eternal life, while the jailer in Acts asks what must be done to be saved.', 'theme', 0.363, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
