(42, 18, 19, 59, 1, 17, 17, 'none is good, save one, that is, God', 'Connection of Goodness and Gifts', 'This connection highlights the concept of goodness as originating from God. Both passages emphasize that true goodness and perfect gifts come from the divine source, reinforcing the idea that God alone embodies goodness.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
