(42, 18, 19, 54, 3, 16, 16, 'none is good, save one, that is, God', 'Nature of Goodness and Godliness', 'This connection highlights the nature of goodness and divinity. In Luke, Jesus emphasizes that only God is truly good, while in 1 Timothy, the manifestation of God in the flesh underscores the divine nature of Jesus, linking goodness with godliness.', 'theme', 0.307, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
