(42, 18, 21, 45, 10, 2, 3, NULL, 'Righteousness and Zeal Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of righteousness and the human effort to achieve it. In Luke, the individual claims to have kept the law, while Romans points out the ignorance of God''s righteousness in favor of establishing one''s own.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
