(42, 18, 22, 40, 19, 21, 21, 'sell all that thou hast, and distribute unto the poor', 'Connection of Jesus'' Instruction', 'Both passages emphasize the command to sell possessions and give to the poor, highlighting a call to discipleship. The promise of treasure in heaven serves as a motivation for this action in both accounts.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
